WEBVTT

00:00:15.647 --> 00:00:17.474
Hello?

00:00:20.442 --> 00:00:22.269
Hello?

00:00:25.781 --> 00:00:30.075
I wondered when
I'd be seeing you, Mr. Potter.

00:00:37.876 --> 00:00:40.082
It seems only yesterday...

00:00:40.337 --> 00:00:46.173
...that your mother and father were
in here buying their first wands.

